precis:
Enactment of an ORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE I TO THE FEDERAL-PROVINCIAL FISCAL
ARRANGEMENTS ACT by adding thereto the names of the four PORT AUTHORITIES
listed below, effective July 1, 1999.
.
1. Nanaimo Port Authority      * Administration portuaire de Nanaïmo
2. North Fraser Port Authority * Administration portuaire du North-Fraser
3. Port Alberni Port Authority * Administration portuaire de Port-Alberni
4. Thunder Bay Port Authority  * Administration portuaire de Thunder Bay
.
